bsent. By its absence it creates a vacuum into which the dream world + the dream \"I\" come. + this fits in with my is minute reminder dream of the AI voice as set up in advance to awaken me to the recollection of the situation. Anamnesis + the meta-abstraction are not two things, then, one cause + one effect but are epitomize by the in-rushing - not just of Acts - but of Thomas primarily: world the because there is a self whose world it is. term \"Ditheon\" then expresses the notion of a qualitative difference between the state of returned self + the dream state, just as in dream the dream self, the \"it is not real a in the sense or degree that the waking self is it is a phantom self, merely there for the purpose of perception of the dream; one could say that the dream created it, rather than it 201 the dream. Dream + it are, then, alike, but Ditheon is of another, higher order. is Ditheon\" a metaphor to depict qualitative difference, rather than accrued quantity + yet, oddly, in that dream it is clear that the advertitious psyche pouring in is a man + not God or the Holy Spirit or Christ. Well, the dreamer wakes up + is a man. But the dream self which it is supposes itself to be a man is not the two-psyche \"bilateral only simulated. Hemispheric parity\" superman is, then, someone asleep into whom the genuine waking self - + is able or psyche or ego has returned to say \"anokhi.\" not because it has become conscious through evolution but has become conscious through waking up - i.e. conscious again Well, this certainly would explain the Acts material in \"Tears\"? The Holy Spirit didn't put it there; no: in my sleep I slightly remembered my waking life + world. Acts, then, is not the past; it is outside intruding on the dream + dreamer. Which is why wrote recently, \"I didn't see the world t of the past, 70 AD; I saw the world of the Bible.\" now, herein fits \"He causes things to look different so it'd appear time ha passed,\" which always struck me as uniquely