      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n127\nNeeds Review\n127\n265 that Valis was from the future. This speculation appears in \"Valis\" + is speci fically identified as \"H. Fat's progeny highly evolved.\") Hence when Valis was present I experienced a dysfunction in time, in fact time seemingly flowing backward good heavens; in \"Valis\" I speak of \"interspecies symbiosis I (the crossbonding that produces the homoplasmate.) + have I not perceived angel Archer as supremely rational? This for me wou",
      "matched_alias": "Archer",
      "term_id": "TERM_archer",
      "term_name": "Archer",
      "term_slug": "archer"
    },
    {
      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n128\nNeeds Review\n128\nK266 contrary, a more evolved mind imposed it. self on me using me - to create itself, t I now think. Then Thomas + I are \"DI\" but not \"theon\"; \"theon\" results from us but we remain human. In the first version of \"Valis\" I end with a long weird study of this, + it would seem to be verified by \"BTA.\" Russ' letter + the Ditheon in dream \"He has been transplanted would refer to a human psyche. Thomas, but \"+ is alive\" signifies \"is a",
